data.title: Bookmobile Special Visit: Silver Birch Lodge
data.meta_description: In addition to the regular weekly schedule, the Bookmobile visits senior's lodges, complexes and apartments every three weeks throughout Strathcona County. Silver Birch Lodge is located at 910 Bison Way, Sherwood Park.
